BBEX3.A.IQD.EUR.CA.AC.A04: Exchange rates for the euro in Iraq / EUR 1 = IQD ... (middle)
Source: Central Bank of Iraq, Baghdad
Methodology: Calculated on the basis of month-end buying and selling rates.
Comment on 2004: Calculated on the basis of month-end rates for the US dollar in Iraq in conjunction with the ECB`s euro reference rate for the US dollar.
